---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="ZenMerch"
  description="ZenMerch is a Shopify product personalization app that helps merchants sell customizable products with live preview, validation, templates + targeting, webhooks/exports, and OS2 theme integration."
>
  <section class="container-pad py-14 sm:py-20">
    <div class="grid gap-10 lg:grid-cols-12 lg:items-center">
      <div class="lg:col-span-7">
        <div class="reveal" data-reveal>
          <p class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.03] px-3 py-1 text-xs text-white/70">
            ZenMerch · Shopify app
          </p>
          <h1 class="mt-5 text-balance text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight sm:text-5xl">
            Personalization made powerful, simple, and instant.
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-2xl text-pretty text-base text-white/70 sm:text-lg">
            ZenMerch helps merchants sell customizable products with a fast, user-friendly product page personalizer—built for Online Store 2.0
            and production-ready operations.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/products/zenmerch/demo">See demo</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/products/zenmerch/features">Features</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/products/zenmerch/docs">Docs</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <div class="card reveal overflow-hidden p-5" data-reveal>
          <img
            class="w-full rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02]"
            src="/images/zenmerch/zenmerch-hero.jpg"
            alt="ZenMerch storefront personalized product"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
          <div class="mt-5 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 text-xs text-white/70">
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-3">
              <div class="font-semibold text-white">Personalizer Builder</div>
              <div class="mt-1">Fields + layers</div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-3">
              <div class="font-semibold text-white">Live preview</div>
              <div class="mt-1">Instant updates</div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-3">
              <div class="font-semibold text-white">Templates</div>
              <div class="mt-1">Reuse at scale</div>
            </div>
            <div class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-3">
              <div class="font-semibold text-white">OS 2.0 integration</div>
              <div class="mt-1">Theme app blocks</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-5 flex gap-2">
            <a class="btn btn-secondary w-full" href="/products/zenmerch/features">All features</a>
            <a class="btn btn-primary w-full" href="/contact">Book a call</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-pad pb-14 sm:pb-20">
    <div class="reveal" data-reveal>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">How it works</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-sm text-white/65">
        A clean workflow designed for conversion and production.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">1) Install + add blocks</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">Enable the embed and place the app block on product templates (OS 2.0).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">2) Build templates</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">Create fields + layers, link them, then reuse via templates and targeting rules.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card p-6">
          <div class="text-sm font-semibold">3) Fulfill at scale</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-white/65">Use webhooks + CSV-friendly exports for batching and production workflows.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="container-pad pb-20">
    <div class="card reveal p-8 md:p-10" data-reveal>
      <div class="grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 md:items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Explore everything ZenMerch offers</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-white/65">
            Image-led feature explanations, pricing, public documentation, and FAQ—built for Shopify reviewers and merchants.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/products/zenmerch/features">Features</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/products/zenmerch/faq">FAQ</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="grid gap-3">
          <a class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 text-sm text-white/75 hover:bg-white/[0.05]" href="/products/zenmerch/pricing">
            <div class="font-semibold text-white">Pricing</div>
            <div class="mt-1">Plans designed for early-stage and growth stores.</div>
          </a>
          <a class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 text-sm text-white/75 hover:bg-white/[0.05]" href="/products/zenmerch/docs">
            <div class="font-semibold text-white">Documentation</div>
            <div class="mt-1">Public docs suitable for Shopify review and merchant onboarding.</div>
          </a>
          <a class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 text-sm text-white/75 hover:bg-white/[0.05]" href="/products/zenmerch/docs/getting-started">
            <div class="font-semibold text-white">Getting started</div>
            <div class="mt-1">Install, enable theme embed, add block, create template, target products.</div>
          </a>
          <a class="rounded-xl border border-white/10 bg-white/[0.02] p-4 text-sm text-white/75 hover:bg-white/[0.05]" href="/products/zenmerch/demo">
            <div class="font-semibold text-white">Demo</div>
            <div class="mt-1">A quick walk-through of what ZenMerch looks like in-store.</div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

